| Q2 | Provider-repo `getProvidersMeta()` API for the observerвҖҷs wiring вҖ” pull-listener vs push-listener? | push-listener via small `providerResultEmitter` bus (zero coupling) |
| Q3 | Anomaly detection method (IQR isolation vs EWMA control chart vs Holt-Winters) | IQR isolation (simple, deterministic, matches existing math) |

